You will need original files to play, read the README for instructions.

Savestates default path is now /usr/local/home/.bermudasyndrome.

Controls are:
D-Pad = Move (character and selection in bag/dialogs)
A = Use selected weapon
B = Action, skip dialog/video and selection option in bag/dialog
X = Show status
Y = Run and hide weapon
SELECT = Quit game
START = Show bag and select option
L = Load game
R = Save game
